{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125088965775331328012684.jpeg/N8SSHdsf8Hsk-Jl7nyccSmg9wdSnFvBAcxaN8HMWjfA\" alt=\"方力申與寶貝女兒勁有父女相！（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申與寶貝女兒勁有父女相！（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260131/1094345734519525376806124.jpeg/AZYNhqU96tH32323q0r8FHFW-CKEnEQ7ore4AqK3uAI\" alt=\"方力申自從做爸爸後就變成曬B狂魔。（方力申微博圖片）\"><figcaption>方力申自從做爸爸後就變成曬B狂魔。（方力申微博圖片）</figcaption></figure><p>方力申開心「些牙」與寶貝BB女互動片</p><p>如今小BB女已4個多月大，而新手爸爸方力申更化身「女兒奴」，經常在Instagram上分享與寶貝女的互動。早前分享完替BB女清潔的短片，昨日又分享與玩耍的時光，還哄得女兒開心大笑。今日（4月26日）也分享了與女兒臉貼臉的大頭相，十分有父女相！網民都激讚BB女可愛：「好得意呀」、「囡囡連眼神都似埋爸爸」、「真係好冧」。陳敏之更說：「咁樣點出到門口」。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089444022456320560739.jpeg/Ga86IkNBejOUn8eqBX7eY8bSF3jfQ5_BaGgP32hoD98\" alt=\"方力申與寶貝女兒（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申與寶貝女兒（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089455955775488934718.jpeg/MsM7bJzLlj8xBrAe_AGYdyLoM7uKHBIzpPUcsKT1HLA\" alt=\"方力申替寶貝女兒清潔。（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申替寶貝女兒清潔。（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089453762023424876902.jpeg/H2YvyvO7_BkjRZhLU-MpCL0j6wT-dwNbOYHhKzmB4Ss\" alt=\"方力申與女兒玩遊戲。（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申與女兒玩遊戲。（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089451182395392491623.jpeg/gqHphZn9-9_UgtEp-KdhALLfhjebiqVl6vBhaerwYWk\" alt=\"方力申與女兒玩遊戲。（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申與女兒玩遊戲。（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089449005420544621389.jpeg/d3BsJU_U-c1DyDGnfweJTkkcZbVOLVAesbW1NrG1tTY\" alt=\"方力申與女兒「餅印」一樣。（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申與女兒「餅印」一樣。（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260426/1125089446291574784431072.jpeg/DRQe59oAZfJbJ-blOH8C4I95TKlJkORUCknLHwpJyx8\" alt=\"方力申個女真係勁可愛！（ig@alexfongliksun）\"><figcaption>方力申個女真係勁可愛！（ig@alexfongliksun）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-26T11:38:56.991901+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":438,"images":8,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}